room_title: Escape room "Carnival Macabre" by Escape-topia in Miami
room_description: You and some friends are at a carnival in your hometown. Sneaking backstage just for fun, you find yourselves in the living quarters of Giggles the Clown. But something isn't right. Giggles is clearly disturbed, will you solve the mystery of this demented clown before he returns and catches you in his room?
